
GERB2TIFF 
====================================================================
utility to generate raster graphics bitmap from Gerber RS274X files.


Package contents
--------------------------

File/path                Description
----------------------------------------------------------
aclocal.m4            
ChangeLog            List of changes to each version release
configure
configure.ac
COPYING              GNU General Publuc Lisence
INSTALL              General Installation Instructions
Makefile.am         
Makefile.in
NEWS
README   		     This file 
build-aux/           Auxilary programs for configure
src/                 Source files
html/                Documentation
examples/            Examples of RS274X gerber files 




Documention
--------------------------

All the documentation is in HTML in the html directory.  
To view the documentation point your favourite WWW viewer at html/index.html;


Install
--------------------------
See INSTALL for general install instructions.
Basically what you want to do is:

    % ./configure
    % make
    % su
    % make install


Dependencies
--------------------------
Libraries:

    libtiff - version 3.9.1 or later. Available from http://www.libtiff.org/
    
    

